  "text": "FRT40A spen 9E34 [allele presents a nonsense mutation (C>T at genome position ; is a truncated, active version of intracellular Notch [CITATION_1] . UAS-EGFR-DN (the 3 rd chromosome of BL5364 was used) The spen rescue experiment was performed using the pACMAN construct CH321-56B18 from [CITATION_2] , inserted on the 3 chromosomes attP-76A2. UAS-spen7R-NAi, gift from I. ",
